qDef.qDef:
Num
(
   
      (Sum({$<[Sales Type]={'Net Sales'},[Business Unit] -= {'Printing Services'}, [Month ID] = {"<=$(v_Max_Month_ID)"}, Year = {$(v_Max_Year)} , [Currency Sorting Key]={$(=MaxString([Currency Sorting Key]))}>}[Invoice Amount USD]*[Currency Average Rate]) 
      -Sum({$<[Sales Type]={'Net Sales'},[Business Unit] -= {'Printing Services'}, [Month ID] = {"<=$(v_Max_Month_ID)"}, Year = {$(v_Max_Year)} , [Currency Sorting Key]={$(=MaxString([Currency Sorting Key]))}>}[Invoice Cost USD]*[Currency Average Rate]) )/Sum([Invoice MT])
   
    ,
    Text
    (
      Pick
      (
          $(v_Selected_Measure_Four)
          ,
          '#,##0' & ' COP/MT'
          ,
         '#,##0'  &' ASP/MT'
          ,
         '#,##0.00'  &' COP %'


      )
   )
   , '.' , ',' )
